-spec find_high_access_employees(Access_times :: [[unicode:unicode_binary()]]) -> [unicode:unicode_binary()].
find_high_access_employees(Access_times) ->
    Prepared = lists:foldl(fun([Name, Time], Acc) ->
                               TimeInt = list_to_integer(binary_to_list(Time)),
                               case maps:find(Name, Acc) of
                                 {ok, Times} -> maps:update(Name, [TimeInt | Times], Acc);
                                 error -> maps:put(Name, [TimeInt], Acc)
                               end
                           end, #{}, Access_times),
    HighAccess = maps:fold(fun(Name, Times, Acc) ->
                               SortedTimes = lists:usort(Times),
                               HighAccess = check_times(SortedTimes, []),
                               case HighAccess of
                                 true -> [Name | Acc];
                                 false -> Acc
                               end
                           end, [], Prepared),
    lists:usort(HighAccess).

check_times([First, Second, Third | Rest], _) when Third - First =< 60 ->
    true;
check_times([_ | Rest], Acc) ->
    check_times(Rest, Acc);
check_times(_, _) ->
    false.
